test.run_tests module#

runs a series of tests using the pytest framework.

Collecting and reporting code coverage data, generating a coverage report in both text and HTML formats.

test.run_tests.run_tests()[source]#

Run pytest tests and generates code coverage reports.

Returns:

The exit code from the pytest tests.

int
